1
00:00:13,166 --> 00:00:14,916
[ALFONSO]
Upon my sword I vow.

2
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,833
We will rid our
fair country of Mendoza.

3
00:00:17,916 --> 00:00:20,333
Come. Let us so swear.

4
00:00:20,416 --> 00:00:22,333
[LEÓN] If they're holding
the queen inside the castle,

5
00:00:22,416 --> 00:00:23,666
do you know where she'd be?

6
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:25,125
[ALFONSO]
I want my mother freed,

7
00:00:25,208 --> 00:00:27,208
but I returned
to save Valiante.

8
00:00:27,291 --> 00:00:29,583
My land must come first.

9
00:00:29,666 --> 00:00:33,000
[MENDOZA] A moon in crimson,
as if soaked in blood.

10
00:00:33,083 --> 00:00:35,583
It heralds the beast
that shall lead this world

11
00:00:35,666 --> 00:00:37,791
to the purifying flame.

12
00:00:37,875 --> 00:00:40,375
Even the strength of
your mighty Watchdog Council

13
00:00:40,458 --> 00:00:44,291
is as nothing.
All will flee before it!

14
00:02:27,041 --> 00:02:28,541
[LEÓN grunts]

15
00:02:30,625 --> 00:02:34,708
[ALFONSO yells]

16
00:02:38,666 --> 00:02:41,083
The summoning of the
Blood Moon is almost complete,

17
00:02:41,166 --> 00:02:43,791
you uncouth children.
It's too late.

18
00:02:43,875 --> 00:02:45,500
[LEÓN growls]

19
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:47,750
[ALFONSO] León!
Don't worry about Mendoza!

20
00:02:47,833 --> 00:02:49,375
We have a bigger target!

21
00:02:49,458 --> 00:02:51,791
[HORROR 11A growls]

22
00:02:53,458 --> 00:02:55,125
The witch's progeny.

23
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:58,583
Born amidst the screams
of your immolated mother.

24
00:02:58,666 --> 00:03:00,375
What a pleasure
to meet you at last.

25
00:03:00,458 --> 00:03:01,708
[LEÓN grunts]

26
00:03:01,791 --> 00:03:04,541
You murdered her,
you monster!

27
00:03:04,625 --> 00:03:05,833
Careful, boy.

28
00:03:05,916 --> 00:03:07,875
Drawing strength
from a personal vendetta

29
00:03:07,958 --> 00:03:10,208
does not become
a knight, you know.

30
00:03:13,125 --> 00:03:15,583
[LEÓN yells]

31
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,541
[LEÓN grunts]

32
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:22,416
You burn as well.

33
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:26,791
[ALFONSO grunts]
León!

34
00:03:30,541 --> 00:03:31,916
[LEÓN]
What the--?

35
00:03:35,416 --> 00:03:36,791
[ALFONSO]
León?

36
00:03:40,916 --> 00:03:42,375
[LEÓN grunts]

37
00:03:45,416 --> 00:03:47,416
[LEÓN gasps]

38
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:49,083
Mother?

39
00:03:49,166 --> 00:03:52,375
[HORROR 11A growls]

40
00:03:52,458 --> 00:03:54,000
[ALFONSO]
Cousin!

41
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:57,125
[MENDOZA] You don't
remember her death.

42
00:03:57,208 --> 00:04:00,083
How could you?
You were but seconds old.

43
00:04:00,166 --> 00:04:01,625
So I'll show you.

44
00:04:01,708 --> 00:04:03,833
Observe as your
dear mother is consumed,

45
00:04:03,916 --> 00:04:05,916
as the very flesh
which housed your body

46
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:09,083
burns away and her bones
crack and blacken.

47
00:04:09,166 --> 00:04:10,625
[LEÓN]
Don't do this.

48
00:04:13,291 --> 00:04:14,916
[MENDOZA] I imagine
your father told you

49
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,208
her suffering was
the thing of a moment.

50
00:04:17,291 --> 00:04:20,500
Sadly, nothing could
be more false.

51
00:04:20,583 --> 00:04:22,083
[ANNA]
I'm burning! I'm burning!

52
00:04:22,166 --> 00:04:24,666
Oh, God. Somebody save me!

53
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:28,833
Please, I'll do anything!
I don't wanna die like this!

54
00:04:28,916 --> 00:04:30,333
[LEÓN]
No!

55
00:04:30,416 --> 00:04:33,250
[ALFONSO] Don't believe
Mendoza's lies!

56
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:34,958
He's hitting you
where he knows you to be

57
00:04:35,041 --> 00:04:38,000
most wounded and vulnerable!

58
00:04:38,083 --> 00:04:40,041
[LEÓN breathes shakingly]

59
00:04:40,125 --> 00:04:41,958
No, child of the witch.

60
00:04:42,041 --> 00:04:46,416
I deliver you naught
but the truth. See?

61
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:48,875
Though she's hardly
recognizable now,

62
00:04:48,958 --> 00:04:51,416
watch carefully your
mother's fiery demise.

63
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:52,583
[MALE SUBJECT 1E]
Death to the witch!

64
00:04:52,666 --> 00:04:54,166
[MALE SUBJECT 1F]
Burn for all eternity!

65
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:56,541
[FEMALE SUBJECT 1C] This is for
my daughter, you monster!

66
00:04:56,625 --> 00:05:04,666
[LEÓN yelling]

67
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:07,625
[screams]

68
00:05:08,916 --> 00:05:11,375
[HORROR 11A growls]

69
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:15,791
[ALFONSO] León! Cousin!
Snap out of it!

70
00:05:15,875 --> 00:05:20,875
[ANNA]
León. My darling baby.

71
00:05:20,958 --> 00:05:23,041
[LEÓN gasps]

72
00:05:23,125 --> 00:05:28,541
[ZARUBA inhales]

73
00:05:38,083 --> 00:05:40,500
[GERMÁN]
Mm. Damn it!

74
00:05:40,583 --> 00:05:43,375
Don't you dare succumb. León!

75
00:05:46,541 --> 00:05:50,750
[ALFONSO grunting]

76
00:05:53,583 --> 00:05:55,791
[LEÓN growls]

77
00:05:55,875 --> 00:05:57,125
[ALFONSO]
Impossible!

78
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:58,958
[MENDOZA]
A thing of beauty.

79
00:05:59,041 --> 00:06:00,375
[ALFONSO]
What have you done?

80
00:06:00,458 --> 00:06:02,375
I just lit the kindling.

81
00:06:02,458 --> 00:06:04,583
What you see now
is the true form

82
00:06:04,666 --> 00:06:08,166
of the Golden Armor,
replete with hatred.

83
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:11,666
It's a testament to the
worst in the human heart.

84
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:14,458
[ALFONSO]
Mendoza! You bastard!

85
00:06:14,541 --> 00:06:23,208
[HORROR 11A growling]

86
00:06:25,583 --> 00:06:33,708
--[LEÓN grunting]
--[HORROR 11A groaning]

87
00:06:33,791 --> 00:06:37,500
[ALFONSO] How? How can
this gold-plated beast

88
00:06:37,583 --> 00:06:39,625
be the Garo of before?

89
00:06:39,708 --> 00:06:44,708
[LEÓN growling]

90
00:06:46,625 --> 00:06:48,458
[ALFONSO] Oh, no!
He's heading into town!

91
00:06:48,541 --> 00:06:50,000
León! Wait!

92
00:06:51,208 --> 00:06:52,750
[MENDOZA] It would seem
the Makai Knights

93
00:06:52,833 --> 00:06:54,791
aren't what they used to be.

94
00:06:54,875 --> 00:06:59,125
A pity, but our plans will
see fruition all the sooner.

95
00:07:04,791 --> 00:07:06,583
Very soon.

96
00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:14,916
[LEÓN roars]

97
00:07:18,958 --> 00:07:21,666
[CROWD screaming]

98
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,083
[ALFONSO]
Snap out of it, León!

99
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:25,916
The capital
will not survive this!

100
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,375
Aah!

101
00:07:32,791 --> 00:07:38,208
[breathing deeply]

102
00:07:40,208 --> 00:07:42,500
[CROWD screaming]

103
00:07:42,583 --> 00:07:44,958
Here! These will
protect you a bit!

104
00:07:47,375 --> 00:07:49,791
[grunting]

105
00:07:50,958 --> 00:07:52,666
Hurry, everyone!

106
00:07:58,625 --> 00:08:03,250
This devil's the
legendary Knight of Light?

107
00:08:03,333 --> 00:08:05,791
Valiante's savior?

108
00:08:05,875 --> 00:08:07,458
[LEÓN roars]

109
00:08:07,541 --> 00:08:09,583
[ALFONSO] This night,
he'll be the death of us all!

110
00:08:12,833 --> 00:08:15,708
[ALFONSO] He gives free reign
to his lust for vengeance.

111
00:08:15,791 --> 00:08:18,541
How easily he abandons
his duty to the people

112
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:21,916
he's sworn to protect!

113
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:25,541
León! With my sword
in hand, I defy you!

114
00:08:25,625 --> 00:08:27,958
Come what may!

115
00:08:28,041 --> 00:08:30,500
Uncle, forgive what
I am to do!

116
00:08:30,583 --> 00:08:34,416
Your son is mad with rage!
Do not try to stop me.

117
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:36,125
[GERMÁN]
The emblem at his waist.

118
00:08:36,208 --> 00:08:37,416
[ALFONSO gasps]

119
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,291
Hit the Makai emblem.

120
00:08:39,375 --> 00:08:41,958
That should dispel
the Golden Armor.

121
00:08:42,041 --> 00:08:44,291
Strike with all your might.

122
00:08:44,375 --> 00:08:47,291
You have to hit hard enough
to run him through.

123
00:08:49,125 --> 00:08:50,375
It should be me.

124
00:08:50,458 --> 00:08:53,625
It's a father's duty
to discipline his son.

125
00:08:53,708 --> 00:08:56,041
Uh! Were it not
for this shoulder,

126
00:08:56,125 --> 00:08:58,458
I'd kill him myself.

127
00:08:58,541 --> 00:09:00,791
Do it. Please.

128
00:09:00,875 --> 00:09:03,791
While he still has
a soul left to redeem.

129
00:09:06,416 --> 00:09:08,666
Yes, Uncle.

130
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:11,958
León, how could you
be so numb?

131
00:09:12,041 --> 00:09:14,666
Even to the words
of your own father.

132
00:09:15,583 --> 00:09:19,125
[LEÓN gasps]
Mother!

133
00:09:19,208 --> 00:09:20,583
Mother!

134
00:09:27,541 --> 00:09:33,458
[crying]

135
00:09:33,541 --> 00:09:36,375
[screams]

136
00:09:38,416 --> 00:09:41,458
León, that's enough!

137
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:45,458
[LEÓN growls]

138
00:09:59,458 --> 00:10:02,208
[MENDOZA] If all Makai Knights
and Alchemists were as foolish

139
00:10:02,291 --> 00:10:05,333
as this pair, I would have
been content to let nature

140
00:10:05,416 --> 00:10:08,625
take its course and have them
kill each other off.

141
00:10:08,708 --> 00:10:10,333
[ALFONSO grunts]

142
00:10:10,416 --> 00:10:13,000
[LEÓN roars]

143
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:15,250
[GERMÁN gasps]

144
00:10:21,333 --> 00:10:23,875
[ALFONSO]
Santa Bard!

145
00:10:23,958 --> 00:10:25,333
[grunts]

146
00:10:27,333 --> 00:10:30,541
[ALFONSO] I will save you!
Capital and kingdom alike!

147
00:10:30,625 --> 00:10:32,875
I will preserve them both!

148
00:10:35,041 --> 00:10:36,125
[ALFONSO]
Stand down, León!

149
00:10:36,208 --> 00:10:38,708
Heap no more sins
atop your head!

150
00:10:38,791 --> 00:10:40,916
[LEÓN growls]

151
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,708
[ALFONSO grunts]

152
00:10:42,791 --> 00:10:47,291
[LEÓN growls]

153
00:10:52,416 --> 00:10:54,500
Just look at what
you've become, chico!

154
00:10:54,583 --> 00:10:56,000
I preferred the old you!

155
00:10:56,083 --> 00:10:57,625
[ALFONSO]
Miss Ema!

156
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,583
[LEÓN roars]

157
00:11:03,958 --> 00:11:07,083
[LEÓN roars]

158
00:11:08,291 --> 00:11:10,333
[ALFONSO yells]

159
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,333
[ALFONSO grunts]

160
00:11:22,416 --> 00:11:25,333
[LEÓN roars]

161
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:36,583
[ALFONSO yells]

162
00:11:56,416 --> 00:11:58,333
[ALFONSO grunts]

163
00:12:08,583 --> 00:12:10,375
My son.

164
00:12:13,416 --> 00:12:15,708
[gasps]
León!

165
00:12:21,833 --> 00:12:25,291
[GERMÁN] Forgive me.
You always burned.

166
00:12:25,375 --> 00:12:29,791
But I never knew a way
to put the flames out.

167
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:33,208
[yells]

168
00:12:34,708 --> 00:12:36,125
[LEÓN]
Blaaahhh!

169
00:12:37,625 --> 00:12:39,041
[LEÓN grunts]

170
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:42,875
[LEÓN laughs]

171
00:12:44,083 --> 00:12:46,125
[groans]

172
00:12:55,416 --> 00:12:58,541
[GERMÁN]
Anna. I am sorry.

173
00:13:08,875 --> 00:13:11,583
Germán!
Get up off your ass!

174
00:13:12,916 --> 00:13:14,750
León!

175
00:13:18,416 --> 00:13:19,791
[GERMÁN grunts]

176
00:13:21,791 --> 00:13:23,541
León!

177
00:13:25,833 --> 00:13:28,625
[gasps, exhales]

178
00:13:32,666 --> 00:13:34,916
[GERMÁN]
You held back, Alfonso?

179
00:13:37,541 --> 00:13:40,166
I attacked with every
bit of strength I had.

180
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:45,833
[HORROR 11A growls]

181
00:13:45,916 --> 00:13:47,958
Better late than never.

182
00:13:52,250 --> 00:13:56,041
[HORROR 11A growls lowly]

183
00:13:56,125 --> 00:13:59,583
Good uncle, the blood
of the Golden Knight Garo

184
00:13:59,666 --> 00:14:02,083
flows through my veins,
as well as León's.

185
00:14:02,166 --> 00:14:03,250
[gasps]

186
00:14:03,333 --> 00:14:06,041
That I may protect
the people of Valiante!

187
00:14:09,375 --> 00:14:12,375
O Father. Mother mine.

188
00:14:12,458 --> 00:14:14,916
Be with me in this dark hour!

189
00:14:22,666 --> 00:14:24,375
[ALFONSO grunts]

190
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,833
How many Golden Knights
is it now?

191
00:14:31,916 --> 00:14:35,583
Their tenure's so short,
it's hard to keep count.

192
00:14:35,666 --> 00:14:38,166
[ALFONSO] Know that
I will be the last!

193
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:40,333
[LEÓN groans softly]

194
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:08,666
[ALFONSO yells]

195
00:15:21,708 --> 00:15:24,583
You're right about
being the last one.

196
00:15:24,666 --> 00:15:27,500
And now, you will languish
in the belly of that beast

197
00:15:27,583 --> 00:15:31,166
as it wanders Makai
for all eternity.

198
00:15:48,291 --> 00:15:52,208
My goodness.
How soon they grow up.

199
00:15:52,291 --> 00:15:54,416
To think that I once
held you in my arms

200
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,625
when you were but a babe.

201
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:15,583
[HORROR 11A groans]

202
00:16:36,416 --> 00:16:38,083
[LEÓN groans]

203
00:16:39,375 --> 00:16:42,958
My armor.
Give it back to me.

204
00:16:43,041 --> 00:16:45,916
Son, that armor is not
yours to take back.

205
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,125
Not anymore.

206
00:16:47,208 --> 00:16:50,083
Alfonso is its new
lord and master.

207
00:16:51,625 --> 00:16:54,000
What became of Mendoza?

208
00:16:54,083 --> 00:16:58,500
He's dead, León.
No doubt about it.

209
00:16:58,583 --> 00:17:03,291
So... I was useless?

210
00:17:08,083 --> 00:17:11,708
[LEÓN]
Give it back. Please.

211
00:17:11,791 --> 00:17:13,708
Give me back the armor!

212
00:17:16,041 --> 00:17:18,291
Garo belongs to me!

213
00:17:20,125 --> 00:17:21,541
Give it back!

214
00:17:21,625 --> 00:17:23,333
[ALFONSO]
You want it back,

215
00:17:23,416 --> 00:17:26,458
while the city of
our birth lies in flames?

216
00:17:26,541 --> 00:17:28,041
Look around!

217
00:17:28,125 --> 00:17:31,916
Mendoza didn't do this with
the Horrors at his command.

218
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,125
It was you!

219
00:17:33,208 --> 00:17:34,875
[LEÓN gasps]

220
00:17:34,958 --> 00:17:38,666
Santa Bard suffers
because of you!

221
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:42,000
I'm to believe that you can
be trusted as a Makai Knight

222
00:17:42,083 --> 00:17:44,500
to safeguard the lives
of the innocent?

223
00:17:46,958 --> 00:17:49,708
[LEÓN] My mother.
It's all I have of her!

224
00:17:49,791 --> 00:17:52,041
[GERMÁN]
God damn it!

225
00:17:52,125 --> 00:17:53,583
That is enough!

226
00:17:55,666 --> 00:17:57,041
Don't you get it, León?

227
00:17:57,125 --> 00:18:00,125
You're a member of the
Makai Knights no longer!

228
00:18:00,208 --> 00:18:01,916
You need to accept that!

229
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,375
[gasps]

230
00:18:04,875 --> 00:18:09,666
Think about this moment.
How it came to this.

231
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:11,833
And what's next for you.

232
00:18:11,916 --> 00:18:13,875
Figure yourself out,

233
00:18:13,958 --> 00:18:16,916
or you'll spend the rest
of your life on your knees!

234
00:18:21,125 --> 00:18:24,416
If you want it, you'll
have to take it by force.

235
00:18:33,958 --> 00:18:37,041
[ALFONSO] You lack the
courage for even that?

236
00:18:37,125 --> 00:18:40,166
I'm disappointed
sin you, cousin.

237
00:18:44,541 --> 00:18:46,458
[sighs]

238
00:18:51,375 --> 00:18:52,666
What now?

239
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:54,833
A boy cannot
truly become a man

240
00:18:54,916 --> 00:18:58,875
until you let him fall,
and stand up on his own.

241
00:18:58,958 --> 00:19:01,541
Spoken like a man.
[sighs]

242
00:19:01,625 --> 00:19:04,416
You damn Makai Knights
sure are something else.

243
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,833
[chuckles]

244
00:19:05,916 --> 00:19:08,083
Thanks for the help. Really.

245
00:19:10,291 --> 00:19:12,791
[GERMÁN]
Stand up, León.

246
00:19:19,333 --> 00:19:22,416
[XIMENA] Thank goodness.
The fires have burned out!

247
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:25,041
You see?
The worst of it's over.

248
00:19:28,125 --> 00:19:29,333
[MALE SERVANT 12A]
The Prince!

249
00:19:29,416 --> 00:19:31,041
[FEMALE SERVANT 12A]
Master Alfonso!

250
00:19:31,125 --> 00:19:33,916
I am relieved
to see you all well.

251
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,916
[MALE SERVANT 12B] Praise God
you're safe, Highness!

252
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:37,958
What of my
father and mother?

253
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:42,416
Though the King's malady
still leaves him bedridden,

254
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:44,666
he came to no further harm.

255
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:48,083
The Queen was not so fortunate.

256
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:58,000
[door creaks, clangs]

257
00:20:00,875 --> 00:20:03,125
Mother.

258
00:20:03,208 --> 00:20:05,750
Oh, Mother.

259
00:20:10,375 --> 00:20:13,750
[ALFONSO]
Why, Mother? Why this?

260
00:20:13,833 --> 00:20:17,625
Didn't you know that I was
coming back to save you?

261
00:20:17,708 --> 00:20:20,958
[LAURA] She told me her deepest
fear was that Mendoza

262
00:20:21,041 --> 00:20:24,250
would use her
as leverage against you.

263
00:20:24,333 --> 00:20:26,500
When she heard that
you'd returned to Santa Bard,

264
00:20:26,583 --> 00:20:29,125
she dismissed all the servants.

265
00:20:29,208 --> 00:20:32,208
[gasps]
And took her own life.

266
00:20:32,291 --> 00:20:34,916
[sobbing]

267
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,500
Dearest Mother,
I swore I would return here

268
00:20:37,583 --> 00:20:40,500
and set you free.

269
00:20:40,583 --> 00:20:44,583
And now I discover that
your most noble of souls

270
00:20:44,666 --> 00:20:47,041
has gone on to its reward.

271
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:54,541
Please, God!

272
00:20:54,625 --> 00:20:59,333
Please, let her know
peace at last.

273
00:20:59,416 --> 00:21:03,625
[sobbing]

274
00:21:13,958 --> 00:21:16,500
[LEÓN]
What do I do from now on?

275
00:21:16,583 --> 00:21:18,458
I don't know.

276
00:21:18,541 --> 00:21:20,708
I have nothing left.

277
00:21:20,791 --> 00:21:25,125
No armor. No calling.

278
00:21:25,208 --> 00:21:27,500
Mendoza is dead.

279
00:21:27,583 --> 00:21:32,083
So, there's no reason
for me to fight anymore.

280
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:36,291
[XIMENA grunting]

281
00:21:38,750 --> 00:21:41,958
--[distant crash]
--[XIMENA gasps]

282
00:21:42,041 --> 00:21:45,250
[XIMENA] Good sir!
Are you all right? Hey!

283
00:21:45,333 --> 00:21:47,958
[GERMÁN groans]

284
00:21:48,041 --> 00:21:51,541
[ALFONSO] Oh, Mother.
You laid down your sweet life

285
00:21:51,625 --> 00:21:55,583
that Mendoza would
have no sway over me.

286
00:21:55,666 --> 00:22:00,625
León. I chastised you
for your loss of control,

287
00:22:00,708 --> 00:22:04,000
but had it been my mother...

288
00:22:04,083 --> 00:22:07,208
...I daresay I would have
lashed out as well.

289
00:22:22,958 --> 00:22:25,708
[birds cawing]

290
00:24:03,208 --> 00:24:05,041
[GARM] With the dawn,
you awaken to find that

291
00:24:05,125 --> 00:24:07,625
who you are no longer matters.

292
00:24:07,708 --> 00:24:10,875
Of what use are you if you
cannot wield a sword?

